name: JUAN
description: JUAN is a community-driven token centered around a fictional character named Juan and his highly memeable likeness. The project aims to share humor and good vibes through this character and through its online meme generator, which lets community members easily create, vote on, and share memes created by them or by other community members. By making creation and sharing of funny content as easy as possible, JUAN aims to be the "Number Juan Meme" on the internet.
